<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.BrisklyDev.Brisk</id>
  <name>Brisk</name>
  <summary>Ultra-fast, modern download manager for desktop</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0-or-later</project_license>

  <description>
    <p>
      Brisk is a high-speed desktop download manager designed for efficiency and integration with the browser
    </p>
    <p>
      Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Powerful, Custom-Built Download Engine</li>
      <li>Browser Integration</li>
      <li>Downloading video streams from the browser</li>
      <li>Download Queues and Scheduling</li>
      <li>Advanced rules to automatically define file save path based on custom patterns</li>
      <li>Hotkey (ctrl+alt+A) to quickly add a download URL from the clipboard</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

